title: 5e édition du Forum national sur le DNS de l’Antic
description: This seminar aims to build the capacity of the personnel in charge of critical infrastructure and to further optimize the quality of services. The direct impact of this forum will be the improvement of the Internet connection in Cameroon and the enhancement of Internet security. The direct output of this seminar is the resolution of numerous Internet connection problems in Cameroon."

title: How to Find Funders and Partners
description: Webinar organized by Ghana chapter to educate others on how to find funders and partners for their activities.

title: UK Internet Governance Forum 2025
description: One-day event in London focused on “Building Digital Governance Together,” exploring key issues like digital cooperation, trust, innovation, and universal digital rights to shape the future of internet governance in the UK
